    { question: "How much do custom automations cost?", answer: "It depends on complexity. Simple automations (like follow-up sequences) start from a few hundred pounds. More complex systems (like full CRM integrations) cost more. We'll give you a clear, fixed quote before any work begins — no surprises." },
